entry.title: b1-team/superman
entry.summary:
Kill processes protected by antivirus during offensive activities.

superman

Kill everything.

usage

Options:
  -p, --pid <PID>    Pid to kill
  -r                 Recursive kill process
  -t, --time <TIME>  Kill interval time (milliseconds) [default: 500]
  -h, --help         Print help
  -V, --version      Print version

Kill Windows Defender (MsMpEng.exe)

superman.exe -p <PID> -r
